She looked up at Phobia. "I got to go."  She turned and ran out of 
the ship.

She had fear in her eyes as she ran through the trees at top speed.  
She hoped she would get there in time.  She opened her link. "Land 
Mine, I"m coming., Hold on, I'm on my way."
She ran in a full run as fast as her legs would go.  She felt the 
strain on her legs and body, but she had to get there.  She had to 
get to them and save them.  She wouldn't be able to forgiver herself 
if they were killed and she wasn't even there to try to fight for 
them.  

She jumped logs and weaved around trees, praying to the matrix that 
she would get there in time.
